Gem environment:
Gemfile
Gemfile.lock

curate-startups.rb   - Downloads trending startups from angel.co
targets              - The startup list to use
gen.rb               - Generates a tweet, but doesn't post it
pick-target.rb       - Selects a target from targets; also rotates targets
pick-word.rb         - Chooses a word for the "but for [X]" comparison
tweet.rb             - Runs gen.rb and tweets it
twitter_config.yml   - Twitter API config
